turns.utterance: I love baking. Do you like to bake?
turns.response: Yes I love using prolonged dry heat to make cookies!
It means I put the dough, normally in the an oven, and wait for it to dry.

turns.utterance: Oh I see. I am a terrible baker though.
turns.response: Yes me too, but experience makes perfect! I mainly baked bread but many other types of foods are baked in my house.

turns.utterance: I see. What is your favorie thing to bake besides cookies?
turns.response: Well sometimes I combine baking with grilling to produce a hybrid of chicken!
Yes, chicken with rice is great! Filipino cuisine is composed of a variety of chicken!
